[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0879","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0600","title":"网络入侵检测系统 数据包校验和未验证漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理网络数据包时未验证校验和字段的正确性，远程攻击者可通过发送精心构造的畸形数据包绕过 IDS 的检测规则。由于 IDS 与目标主机对数据包的解析结果不一致，攻击者可利用该缺陷隐藏恶意流量，实现绕过告警的入侵行为。该漏洞影响多数未实现校验和验证的 IDS 产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0600"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.743","remediation":"在 IDS/IPS 配置中启用 IP 和 TCP 校验和验证功能（如 Snort 的 `config checksum_mode: all`），丢弃校验和错误的报文；升级至支持完整校验和检测的现代 IDS 版本（如 Suricata 7.x 或 Snort 3.x）；在边界防火墙上启用 TCP 校验和强制检查；同时在网络设备上启用 IP 选项过滤和分片重组校验，消除攻击者利用校验和绕过检测的路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0600","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0600.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86246/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0878","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0599","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP异常序列号绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理包含异常TCP序列号的数据包时存在逻辑缺陷，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送精心构造的异常序列号数据包绕过IDS的检测与重组机制，导致恶意流量无法被正确识别和告警。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，攻击者无需认证即可远程实施绕过攻击，严重削弱网络安全监控与威胁检测的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0599"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.620","remediation":"升级支持 TCP 流重组（stream reassembly）的入侵检测系统，如 Suricata、Zeek（原名 Bro），并启用 `stream.reassembly` 引擎；禁用纯包级检测的旧式 IDS（如 Snort 1.x 传统模式）。配置 IDS 确保 TCP 分片重组策略与受保护目标主机一致（如设置 `target-based` 策略），避免插包（insertion）和逃逸（evasion）攻击。定期更新检测规则集以覆盖已知逃逸技术。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0599","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0599.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86252/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0876","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0876.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0598","title":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）数据包乱序处理绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理乱序数据包时存在缺陷，无法正确重组和检测经过分片或乱序传输的攻击流量。远程攻击者可通过将恶意负载分散到多个乱序数据包中绕过 IDS 的检测规则，从而逃避安全监控。该漏洞影响多款主流网络入侵检测系统，可被用于隐藏端口扫描、漏洞利用等恶意行为，降低网络防御体系的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0598"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.500","remediation":"配置IDS启用完整的TCP流重组（stream reassembly）功能，确保对乱序IP分片和TCP乱序报文进行正确重组后再执行规则匹配。同时启用分片超时与重组缓冲区限制，防止分片洪水绕过检测。建议使用支持应用层协议解析的现代IDS/IPS（如Snort/Suricata）并开启`stream5`或`stream`预处理模块。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0598","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0598.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hhgq-6w2j-9rc7/GHSA-hhgq-6w2j-9rc7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86249/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0876.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0874","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0597","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 账户策略登录时间限制绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 账户策略存在安全漏洞，当远程用户的登录时间到期后，系统未能强制断开其与服务器的连接，导致用户可在授权时段外继续访问系统资源。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，拥有有效域账户的远程攻击者可利用此问题绕过登录时间限制，在非授权时段持续访问服务器资源，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0597"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.383","remediation":"在 Windows NT 域用户管理器中选择\"规则(Policies)→账户(Account)\"，勾选\"当登录时数到期时强制断开远程用户与服务器的连接(Forcibly disconnect remote users from server when logon hours expire)\"。对于仍运行 Windows NT 的系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，新版本默认启用该策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0597","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0597.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86258/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0872","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0596","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 日志文件大小与保留期限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 日志文件的最大大小或保留期限配置不当，可能导致日志文件无限制增长耗尽磁盘空间，引发拒绝服务；或日志过早轮转覆盖，导致关键安全事件记录丢失，影响事后审计与取证分析。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0596"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.267","remediation":"建议在 Windows NT 事件查看器中右键「事件日志」→「日志设置」，将日志最大大小根据磁盘容量设为 512MB 以上，回卷策略设为「按需要覆盖事件」而非「不要覆盖事件」。若仍使用旧版系统，应升级至 Windows Server 2003 及以上版本以获得完善的日志审计功能。作为临时缓解措施，可设置组策略定期归档并清理旧日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com