s 和 AllocateFloppies 值为 1，限制非管理员用户访问可移动媒体驱动器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0594","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0594.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-788r-28g9-93jm/GHSA-788r-28g9-93jm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86242/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0871.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0870","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0593","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Winlogon 关闭系统无需登录漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 Winlogon 注册表项中 ShutdownWithoutLogon 键值默认设置为启用，允许拥有物理接触权限的未授权用户直接关闭系统而无需登录认证。该漏洞源于系统默认安全配置不当，攻击者仅需物理访问目标主机即可触发关机操作，导致系统可用性受损。影响 Windows NT 系列系统，CVSS 评分 4.9，危害等级中危。建议管理员通过注册表或组策略禁用此功能以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0593"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.887","remediation":"在注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon` 中将 `ShutdownWithoutLogon` 值设为 `0`（REG_SZ），或通过组策略「计算机配置→Windows 设置→安全设置→本地策略→安全选项」启用「关闭系统：仅允许已登录的用户使用关机权限」。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/59333","http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc722469.aspx","http://www.microsoft.com/technet/archive/winntas/deploy/confeat/06wntpcc.mspx?mfr=true","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1291","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0593","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0593.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86243/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0869","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0869.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0592","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 登录用户名信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统登录框默认会显示上一次成功登录的用户名，导致系统敏感信息泄露。本地攻击者通过物理访问目标系统即可获取有效用户名，降低了暴力破解登录密码的难度。该漏洞影响所有 Windows NT 及早期 Windows 版本，攻击者无需任何特权即可利用此漏洞收集账户信息，从而为后续攻击提供便利。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0592"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.777","remediation":"在 Windows NT 中，打开组策略编辑器 (gpedit.msc)，依次展开「计算机配置 → Windows 设置 → 安全设置 → 本地策略 → 安全选项」，将「交互式登录: 不显示上次登录的用户名」设置为「已启用」。也可直接修改注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon`，新建 DWORD 值 `DontDisplayLastUserName` 并设为 `1`。在 Windows Server 2003 及之后版本中此功能已默认启用，无需额外配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1353","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0592","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0592.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6cjr-f6hr-x67r/GHSA-6cjr-f6hr-x67r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86254/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0869.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0865","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0591","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 事件日志权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 事件日志存在不恰当的访问权限配置漏洞，本地普通用户可能能够读取或清除安全事件日志记录。攻击者可利用此漏洞获取系统敏感信息，或在入侵后清理日志痕迹以规避检测。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0591"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.650","remediation":"限制 %SystemRoot%\\System32\\config\\ 目录下 AppEvent.evt、SecEvent.evt、SysEvent.evt 文件的访问权限，仅允许 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 组读取。升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以彻底修复权限配置问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0862","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0589","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表权限漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中关键注册表项存在权限配置不当漏洞，攻击者利用不安全的注册表权限可修改系统关键配置，进而实现本地权限提升或完全控制系统。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限或通过远程获取写入权限后进行利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0589"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.410","remediation":"使用 regedt32.exe 检查并收紧系统关键注册表项（如 HKLM\\SAM、HKLM\\SECURITY、HKLM\\SYSTEM）的 ACL 权限，确保仅 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 拥有完全控制权，移除 Everyone 组的写入权限。同时安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总更新，并在域环境中通过组策略统一加固注册表权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0860","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0860.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0588","title":"OpenSource Router 分片数据包过滤绕过漏洞","description":"路由器或防火墙的包过滤规则未能正确处理异常的 IP 分片数据包，导致攻击者可通过发送特制的分片包绕过访问控制列表或入侵检测系统。该漏洞允许未经认证的远程攻击者绕过安全策略，可能导致信息泄露或服务不可用，影响运行各类开源路由软件及防火墙系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0588"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.290","remediation":"在路由器或防火墙上启用分片包重组与深度检测功能，设置最小分片大小限制，丢弃异常的微小分片包。配置访问控制列表（ACL）对分片包进行精确过滤，防止攻击者利用分片绕过安全策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0588","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0588","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0588.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-56r4-8x77-7j27/GHSA-56r4-8x77-7j27.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0860.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0859","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0587","title":"OpenSource 应用 WWW 服务器文件系统限制绕过漏洞","description":"WWW 服务器未运行在受限文件系统环境中（如未使用 chroot 机制隔离），导致远程攻击者可通过 HTTP 请求直接访问服务器系统关键文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响未正确配置 chroot 环境的各类 WWW 服务器软件，攻击者无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。修复方式为使用 chroot 或容器技术限制 Web 服务的文件系统访问范围。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0587"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.170","remediation":"将 WWW 服务器配置为在 chroot 环境或容器中运行，限制其对 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow 等系统关键文件的访问。修改 Web 服务器配置文件，设置 DocumentRoot 为独立目录，并禁止符号链接跟随 (FollowSymLinks)，同时使用最小权限原则运行服务进程（如 www-data 用户）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822